<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>EBITDA (EBIT) — Official Site</title>
<style>
    :root {
        --bg: #050608;
        --bg-alt: #0f1116;
        --accent: #00e0ff;
        --accent-soft: #00b8d6;
        --text: #ffffff;
        --muted: #a0a4b3;
        --border: #1b1f2a;
    }
    * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #151826 0, #050608 55%);
        color: var(--text);
    }
    a {
        color: inherit;
    }
    header {
        position: sticky;
        top: 0;
        z-index: 20;
        backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(5,6,8,0.96), rgba(5,6,8,0.85));
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .nav {
        max-width: 1120px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 16px;
    }
    .nav-left {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
    }
    .nav-logo {
        width: 40px;
        height: 40px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 20%, #ffffff 0, #c0c4cf 35%, #7f838f 70%, #3a3d45 100%);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        overflow: hidden;
    }
    .nav-logo img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        display: block;
    }
    .nav-title {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        line-height: 1.1;
    }
    .nav-title span:first-child {
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--accent);
    }
    .nav-title span:last-child {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: var(--muted);
    }
    .nav-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 18px;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    .nav-links a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: var(--muted);
        padding: 6px 0;
        border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover {
        color: var(--accent);
        border-bottom-color: var(--accent-soft);
    }
    .nav-cta {
        display: flex;
        gap: 10px;
    }
    .btn {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 9px 18px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        border: 1px solid transparent;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
        cursor: pointer;
        white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .btn-primary {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-soft));
        color: #000;
        box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(0, 224, 255, 0.35);
    }
    .btn-primary:hover {
        filter: brightness(1.05);
    }
    .btn-outline {
        background: transparent;
        color: var(--accent);
        border-color: var(--accent-soft);
    }
    .btn-outline:hover {
        background: rgba(0, 224, 255, 0.08);
    }

    main {
        max-width: 1120px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 40px 20px 80px;
    }

    /* Hero */
    .hero {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 3fr) minmax(0, 2.5fr);
        gap: 40px;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 40px 0 30px;
    }
    .hero-kicker {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.16em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--accent);
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .hero h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 3.2vw, 3.1rem);
        margin: 0 0 14px;
    }
    .hero h1 span {
        color: var(--accent);
    }
    .hero-sub {
        font-size: 0.98rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        max-width: 520px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .hero-meta {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 18px;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        margin-top: 18px;
    }
    .hero-meta span {
        padding: 4px 10px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        background: rgba(10, 12, 18, 0.8);
    }
    .hero-card {
        border-radius: 18px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, #1b2133 0, #090b10 55%);
        padding: 20px 18px;
        box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55);
    }
    .hero-card-header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .hero-card-title {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: var(--muted);
    }
    .hero-card-token {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        font-weight: 600;
    }
    .hero-price {
        font-size: 1.6rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .hero-price span {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        margin-left: 6px;
    }
    .hero-price-placeholder {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    .hero-card-row {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .hero-card-row span:last-child {
        color: var(--accent);
    }

    /* Sections */
    section {
        padding: 40px 0 10px;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(18, 22, 32, 0.9);
        margin-top: 30px;
    }
    section:first-of-type {
        border-top: none;
        margin-top: 0;
    }
    .section-header {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: baseline;
        gap: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .section-header h2 {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        margin: 0;
    }
    .section-header p {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: var(--muted);
    }
    .section-body {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .pill {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 6px;
        padding: 4px 10px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        color: var(--muted);
    }
    .pill-dot {
        width: 7px;
        height: 7px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: var(--accent);
        box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(0, 224, 255, 0.6);
    }

    .grid-2 {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.4fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
        gap: 26px;
    }
    .card {
        border-radius: 16px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        background: var(--bg-alt);
        padding: 18px 18px 16px;
    }
    .card h3 {
        margin: 0 0 10px;
        font-size: 0.98rem;
    }
    .card p {
        margin: 0 0 10px;
        font-size: 0.88rem;
        color: var(--muted);
    }
    .card ul {
        margin: 6px 0 0 18px;
        padding: 0;
        font-size: 0.86rem;
        color: var(--muted);
    }
    .card ul li {
        margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .btn-row {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 10px;
        margin-top: 14px;
    }

    footer {
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        background: #050608;
    }

    @media (max-width: 800px) {
        .hero {
            grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
        }
        .nav-links {
            display: none;
        }
        .nav-cta {
            display: none;
        }
    }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <div class="nav">
        <div class="nav-left">
            <div class="nav-logo">
                <!-- Place ebit-logo.png in same folder -->
                <img src="ebit-logo.png" alt="EBIT logo" />
            </div>
            <div class="nav-title">
                <span>EBITDA • EBIT</span>
                <span>Infrastructure‑backed XRPL utility token</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <nav class="nav-links">
            <a href="#home">Home</a>
            <a href="#whitepaper">Whitepaper</a>
            <a href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
            <a href="#buy">Where to Buy</a>
            <a href="#about">About</a>
        </nav>
        <div class="nav-cta">
            <a class="btn btn-outline" href="#whitepaper">Whitepaper</a>
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#buy">Get EBIT</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</header>

<main>

    <!-- HERO / HOME -->
    <section id="home">
        <div class="hero">
            <div>
                <div class="hero-kicker">XRPL • MULTI‑CHAIN • TELEMETRY</div>
                <h1>EBITDA <span>(EBIT)</span> — infrastructure‑backed utility for real yield.</h1>
                <p class="hero-sub">
                    EBIT is a utility‑driven, data‑powered digital asset built on the XRP Ledger and
                    supported by a multi‑chain backend spanning Bitcoin, Lightning, Cosmos, Stellar,
                    Chainlink, The Graph, and more. Designed for ISO‑aligned financial telemetry and
                    automated value flows.
                </p>
                <div class="btn-row">
                    <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#buy">Launch EBIT flow</a>
                    <a class="btn btn-outline" href="#whitepaper">Read whitepaper</a>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-meta">
                    <span>XRPL native • AMM‑ready</span>
                    <span>ISO‑20022‑aligned telemetry</span>
                    <span>Multi‑chain infrastructure backing
